Downloaded SPECIALIST Lexicon files are added to this directory. Requires
the following files:

    - LEXICON : https://data.lhncbc.nlm.nih.gov/public/lsg/lexicon/2025/release/LEX_DOC/LEXICON
    - LRAGR : https://data.lhncbc.nlm.nih.gov/public/lsg/lexicon/2025/release/LEX_DOC/LRAGR
    - LRNOM : https://data.lhncbc.nlm.nih.gov/public/lsg/lexicon/2025/release/LEX_DOC/LRNOM
    - LRSPL : https://data.lhncbc.nlm.nih.gov/public/lsg/lexicon/2025/release/LEX_DOC/LRSPL
    - LRTRM : https://data.lhncbc.nlm.nih.gov/public/lsg/lexicon/2025/release/LEX_DOC/LRTRM
